<!-- Definition and medical uses -->
'''布比卡因'''（[[國際非專利藥品名稱|國際非專利藥品名稱]]：'''bupivacaine'''，{{pronEng|bjuːˈpɪvəkeɪn}}）是一種氨基酰胺類的[[局部麻醉劑|局部麻醉劑]]。[[阿斯利康製藥|阿斯利康製藥]]以多個商品名稱進行銷售，包括'''Marcain'''、'''Marcaine'''（麻卡因）、'''Sensorcaine'''及'''Vivacaine'''。本品藉由注射於周邊組織以阻斷部分神經，或注射至脊椎孔作硬脊膜外麻醉。<ref name=AHFS2015>{{cite web|title=Bupivacaine Hydrochloride|url=http://www.drugs.com/monograph/bupivacaine-hydrochloride.html|publisher=The American Society of Health-System Pharmacists|accessdate=Aug 1, 2015|archive-date=2015-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150630101203/http://www.drugs.com/monograph/bupivacaine-hydrochloride.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>有一種現成劑型混有[[肾上腺素|肾上腺素]]以達藥效持久之效<!-- <ref name=AHFS2015/> -->；通常在施用後15分後見效，可維持2-8小時。<ref name=AHFS2015/><ref name=Wh1997>{{cite book|last1=Whimster|first1=David Skinner|title=Cambridge textbook of accident and emergency medicine|date=1997|publisher=Cambridge University Press|location=Cambridge|isbn=9780521433792|page=194|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=m0bNaDhkaukC&pg=PA194|access-date=2017-01-06|archive-date=2015-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151005030600/https://books.google.ca/books?id=m0bNaDhkaukC&pg=PA194|dead-url=no}}</ref>

<!-- Side effects and mechanism -->
可能的[[副作用|副作用]]包含嗜睡、肌肉抽搐、耳鳴、視野改變、低血壓及[[心律不整|心律不整]]。<!-- <ref name=AHFS2015/> -->施打於關節部位可能引發軟骨問題，未經稀釋的布比卡因可能延長分娩時間，不建議用於硬脊膜外麻醉。<!-- <ref name=AHFS2015/> -->

<!-- History, society, and culture -->
布比卡因發現於1957年，<ref>{{cite book|last1=Egan|first1=Talmage D.|title=Pharmacology and physiology for anesthesia : foundations and clinical application|date=2013|publisher=Elsevier/Saunders|location=Philadelphia, PA|isbn=9781437716795|page=291|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=s8CXrbimviMC&pg=PT306|access-date=2017-01-06|archive-date=2016-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160512191237/https://books.google.ca/books?id=s8CXrbimviMC&pg=PT306|dead-url=no}}</ref>在最基本的健康照護系統中最必要的藥物清單世界卫生组织基本药物标准清单登錄有案，<ref>{{cite web|title=WHO Model List of EssentialMedicines|url=http://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/10665/93142/1/EML_18_eng.pdf?ua=1|work=World Health Organization|accessdate=22 April 2014|date=October 2013|archive-date=2014-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140423005004/http://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/10665/93142/1/EML_18_eng.pdf?ua=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>作為學名藥也不是十分昂貴，<ref name=AHFS2015/><ref name=Ric2015>{{cite book|last1=Hamilton|first1=Richart|title=Tarascon Pocket Pharmacopoeia 2015 Deluxe Lab-Coat Edition|date=2015|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Learning|isbn=9781284057560|page=22}}</ref>一瓶批發價約在2.10美元左右。<ref name=ERC2015>{{cite web|title=Bupivacaine HCL|url=http://erc.msh.org/dmpguide/resultsdetail.cfm?language=english&code=BUP025A&s_year=2014&year=2014&str=0%2E25%25&desc=Bupivacaine%20HCl&pack=new&frm=AMPOULE&rte=INJ&class_code2=01%2E2%2E&supplement=&class_name=%2801%2E2%2E%29Local%20anaesthetics%3Cbr%3E|website=International Drug Price Indicator Guide|accessdate=29 August 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305062137/http://erc.msh.org/dmpguide/resultsdetail.cfm?language=english&code=BUP025A&s_year=2014&year=2014&str=0%2E25%25&desc=Bupivacaine%20HCl&pack=new&frm=AMPOULE&rte=INJ&class_code2=01%2E2%2E&supplement=&class_name=%2801%2E2%2E%29Local%20anaesthetics%3Cbr%3E|archivedate=2017年3月5日|df=}}</ref>

